data.description: SELLER WILLING TO CONTRIBUTE $10,000 TOWARDS CLOSING COST WITH FULL PRICE OFFER! WELCOME HOME!!! Gorgeous 5 bedroom 3 bathroom 1933 farmhouse with over 4000 square feet located in the heart of downtown Elberton. Conveniently located across the street from the park with tons of walking trails. Situated on a beautiful corner lot with no HOA in the historic district of Elberton. This home features a gourmet kitchen, LVP flooring throughout the home, Oversized master on the main level with a sitting area and luxury bathroom. The master closet is what dreams are made of with TONS of space. The main level also features a secondary bedroom suite with a walk-in closet. Beautiful office with an abundance of natural light overlooking the park! Three additional oversized bedrooms are located upstairs. This home has an oversized 3 car garage with an unfinished bonus room above the garage! Only 8 miles from Lake Russell and just minutes from downtown Elberton!!!
